[The confirmation reported in the preceding news item probably does not
imply confirmation by laboratory testing, since an independent report --
see; Crimean-Congo hem fever - Pakistan (Bal): susp (02) 20040517.1321 --
indicated that samples were on their way to South Africa for further
testing. - Mod.CP]
